text: Alexander Mojžiš (born 2 January 1999) is a professional Slovak footballer who currently plays for Fortuna Liga club Ružomberok as a defender. ==Club career== Alexander has twin brother Viktor, who still plays for Železiarne Podbrezová. ===FK Železiarne Podbrezová=== Alexander Mojžiš made his professional Fortuna Liga debut for Železiarne Podbrezová against ViOn Zlaté Moravce on 19 May 2018 in a 1:0 home win. He played the entire match.PODBREZOVÁ VS.
